        "timestamp": "2017-10-13 06:12:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nHi Ke, As we discuss before, the token request will send to {vio-plugin}/identity/v3, if the domain info in request body, then it's a v3 request, we should send to keystone v3, if the domain info is missing, then it's a v2 request, we should send to keystone v2.0.\n\nvio both support keystone v2.0 and v3 .",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
